---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Research — Teddy Wright">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Research</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">
      My work focuses on AI's impact on labor markets, human information processing,
      and building tools for AI policy.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <article class="border-l-2 border-primary-200 pl-5">
        <span class="text-xs font-medium text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-wider">In Progress</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">LLM Labor Market Impact Dashboard</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Interactive dashboard visualizing LLM labor market impact across 800+ occupations.
          Merges task-level LLM usage data with BLS and ONET occupational data. Includes
          custom imputation and classification pipelines, and a new pipeline mapping agentic
          AI capabilities onto 17,000+ ONET tasks.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">Utah Office of AI Policy · Supervised by Alice Schwarze &amp; Zach Boyd</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border-l-2 border-primary-200 pl-5">
        <span class="text-xs font-medium text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-wider">2026</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">Why Are People Miscalibrated on AI?</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Research poster for AI + Ethics Workshop. Framework: View = Optimization Target
          &times; (Information Quality &times; Processing Quality), with the Self-Concealing
          Property as key insight — identity-protective cognition is phenomenologically
          indistinguishable from rigorous skepticism.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">With Valen Cole · April 2026</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border-l-2 border-gray-200 pl-5">
        <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Upcoming</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">AI in Qualitative Research</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
          SPUR Research Program — exploring how AI can analyze human text and comments
          in research contexts.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">With Vineet Pandey · Summer 2026</p>
      </article>

      <article class="border-l-2 border-gray-200 pl-5">
        <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Contribution</span>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">Project Iceberg</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Nationally recognized AI labor market simulation study.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">Utah Office of AI Policy</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
